snippet.title: Club 3do Station Invasion / 3DO Framemeister S-Video / Full Playthrough
snippet.description:
Played on Panasonic FZ-1 R.E.A.L 3DO  through Framemeister, on a japanese version with embedded Output mode selector; Mode A(480p)/Mode B (240p)
Mode B is the sarphest S-Video I have seen on any system.

Jugado en Panasonic FZ1 R.E.A.L 3DO  a través del Framemeister.
